+    /// Identify the layer group from primitive layer-cell rotations and translations.
+    ///
+    /// Parameters
+    /// ----------
+    /// prim_rotations : list[list[list[int]]]
+    ///     Rotation matrices of the symmetry operations of the primitive layer cell.
+    /// prim_translations : list[list[float]]
+    ///     Translation vectors of the symmetry operations of the primitive layer cell.
+    /// basis : list[list[float]] | None
+    ///     Row-wise basis vectors of the primitive lattice. If ``None``, an identity basis
